    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>SO @NotNull just is a tag...If you want to validate it, then you must use something like hibernate validator jsr 303</p>\n\n<pre><code>ValidatorFactory validatorFactory = Validation.buildDefaultValidatorFactory();\nValidator validator = validatorFactory.getValidator();\n Set&lt;ConstraintViolation&lt;List&lt;Searching&gt;&gt; violations = validator.validate(searchingList);\n</code></pre>\n"
