    "question_id" : 34094039,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To make <code>@NonNull</code> active you need Lombok:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://projectlombok.org/features/NonNull\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://projectlombok.org/features/NonNull</a></p>\n<pre><code>import lombok.NonNull;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Follow: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4963300/which-notnull-java-annotation-should-i-use\">Which @NotNull Java annotation should I use?</a></p>\n"
